Class ActivityWorkerShutdownException

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class ActivityWorkerShutdownException
extends ActivityCompletionException
    Indicates that WorkerFactory.shutdown() or WorkerFactory.shutdownNow() was called. It is OK to ignore the exception to let activity to complete. It assumes that WorkerFactory.awaitTermination(long, TimeUnit) is called with a timeout larger than the activity execution time.
